User Experience Researcher with 1 year of UX research and 8 years of teaching experience seeking a new opportunity. 

Looking to leverage diverse experience leading research projects across the project lifecycle, including planning/design, prepping, facilitating, analysis, and reporting, while working for startup and consulting companies in multiple industries, including Media, Ecommerce, Education, Healthcare, Finance, and Printing. Well-developed skills turning business questions into meaningful customer insights through qualitative and quantitative research methods, conducting start-to-finish usability testing, developing protocol and scripts, facilitating testing, identifying key insights, and presenting results to stakeholders in an engaging way.
